          </div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl text-ink mb-4 leading-tight">The artifact stack collapsed.</h3>
          <p class="text-ink-soft leading-relaxed">
            Wireframe, mock, prototype, spec, handoff. All compressed into one
            prompt-and-judge loop. Fidelity stopped being a phase. The assembly
            line existed because we didn't trust the next station. AI exposed which
            parts of that anxiety were load-bearing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
